{"tid":1169561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[世紀大戰］射鵰黃藥師 vs 倚天楊逍，邊個好打啲？","createTime":"2019-05-24T12:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T17:57:35.000Z","uid":253018,"like":33,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a9918b3e9ade9b04a665e0e7edcde61284297e2a","tid":1169561,"uid":253018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vxgaxh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vxgaxh.png&h=adb1150c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「桃花影落飛神劍，碧海潮生按玉簫」是他一生武功的寫照，武功造詣非凡，已臻化境，為金庸小說中武功最絕頂的高手之一。<br />\n<br />\n在牛家村內與「全真七子」展開激烈交戰，黃藥師在「全真七子」的最大絕學「天罡北斗陣」之下，仍然能憑「落英桃花掌」掌法等高超武功以一敵七維持平手局面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aqaeZq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aqaeZq.png&h=b20ccfc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n六大派圍剿光明頂的時候，因為內鬨的原故，楊逍受到護教法王「青翼蝠王」韋一笑以及五散人圍攻，楊逍更使出明教鎮教之寶「乾坤大挪移」把韋一笑的「寒冰綿掌」反施六人身上，技驚四座。<br />\n<br />\n為救明教四大護教法王之一「金毛獅王」謝遜，隨張無忌並明教四大護教法王之一「白眉鷹王」殷天正合力大戰少林當時輩份最高的少林「三大高僧」渡厄、渡難與渡劫。<br />\n<br />\n黃藥師 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n楊逍 負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c9a299c698f059e967abea52832109bc0545ba","tid":1169561,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"依家香港水深火熱 你仲睇支那小說"},{"pid":"07f1790fd7301028dd311cac389935170bcdc548","tid":1169561,"uid":34241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"落英桃花掌係你發明？"},{"pid":"d5e02e84f2c58d95292226698686d131b522506b","tid":1169561,"uid":253018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:55:20.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"675a2785e6202df21c5fa72b60770e39d412dae9","tid":1169561,"uid":163111,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f2c9a299c698f059e967abea52832109bc0545ba","tid":1169561,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"依家香港水深火熱 你仲睇支那小說"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d623adc790c1d9b698930bc7b3853343175a23c2","tid":1169561,"uid":253018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T16:41:48.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a706031cd1f5242ea2dada7ca1304ef83bfe025c","tid":1169561,"uid":20087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07f1790fd7301028dd311cac389935170bcdc548","tid":1169561,"uid":34241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"落英桃花掌係你發明？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9964cc45e24a685cb05baf34e1390ee96478839","tid":1169561,"uid":143351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2c9a299c698f059e967abea52832109bc0545ba","tid":1169561,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"依家香港水深火熱 你仲睇支那小說"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"讀過書未？"}]}